```html
<div id="condition-container">
  <x-if :value="condition === 'A'">
    <div>I am rendered for condition A.</div>
  </x-if>
  <x-else-if :value="condition === 'B'">
    <div>I am rendered for condition B.</div>
  </x-else-if>
  <x-else>
    <div>I am rendered for other conditions.</div>
  </x-else>
</div>
```